# Compiled binaries and dev artifacts never belong in source — the runnable
# bridge is the one the collector setup installs at
# {setup-root}/solo-agency-local-collector/bin/collector-bridge-{os}-{arch}.
# A committed binary here misleads the agent (wrong OS/arch) and bloats history.
/bridge-go
/bridge-go.exe
/bridge-go_*
*.backup
*.go.bak
